            <p>5566 Germantown Ave July 6<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 83<lb/></p>
            <p>Rev Morais city<lb/></p>
            <p>Dear Sir.<lb/></p>
            <p>I respect you too much I<lb/> have a too great idea of your<lb/> theological lore and your<lb/> uprightness that I should wish<lb/> to continue a public discussion<lb/> with you therefore these <sic>lignes</sic><lb/> <sic>procede</sic> from a strictly orthodox<lb/> view.<lb/></p>
            <p>Do you deny the thalmudical<lb/> saying &#91;Hebrew&#93;<lb/> that in the third century &#91;Hebrew&#93;<lb/> how much less in our time.<lb/>  Now let us accept Simeons met&#45;<lb/>hode.  &#91;Hebrew&#93;  Are these<lb/> man whose marriages I<lb/> bless &#91;Hebrew&#93;&#63;  And if what<lb/> is the punishment.  The Jewish<lb/> park is &#91;Hebrew&#93;<lb/></p>
            <p>But after the rabbis who<lb/> deduced the prohibition of &#91;Hebrew&#93;<lb/> it is a &#91;Hebrew&#93;<lb/> therefore the punish&#45;<lb/>ment &#91;&#63;&#93; &#91;Hebrew&#93;<lb/> over<lb/></p>
                
                <pb n="2"/>
            <p>Now there are people who<lb/> <sic>publicfuly</sic> call &#91;Hebrew&#93;<lb/> who publicly do not part<lb/> on &#91;Hebrew&#93; and therefore<lb/> &#91;Hebrew&#93;  Do you refuse your<lb/> office by their marriages&#63;<lb/>  I will not ask Maimonides<lb/> about &#91;Hebrew&#93;.  I have it not<lb/> to hand.<lb/></p>
            <p>You would say&#44; I think<lb/> these poeple it is to be hoped<lb/> will next time not commit<lb/> such a sin.<lb/></p>
            <p>I say the same&#59; this man<lb/> seeing what true <sic>Judaisme</sic> is will become at least<lb/> a &#91;Hebrew&#93;<lb/></p>
            <p>That I say as orthodox<lb/> as a reform rabbi&#44; I would<lb/> declare the whole reform<lb/> a big <del>ly</del> lie if I would<lb/> act otherwise than I did<lb/> But it is not my province<lb/> to explain to you what<lb/> the reform is<lb/> Truly yours<lb/> Dr Hirsch<lb/></p>
        </body>
